commit.message:
fix(depot-map): Replace MapLibre GL with SVG-based SimpleDepotMap

- Removed non-working MapLibre GL implementation
- Created SimpleDepotMap component with SVG rendering
- Fixed version conflicts with maplibre-gl package
- Added visual regression tests for depot map
- Tracks and trains now render correctly with SVG
- Depot switching works properly
- All 16 tracks with proper color coding
- Train allocations visible as markers
- Added info panel and legend
- Mobile responsive design

BREAKING: Removed MapLibre dependency for now, using pure SVG solution
commit.author: Christian Schmeing
